data.description: Check out this two story home located on the North end of Zanesville. Home has a one car garage in the rear. Main floor offers a large living room, dining room, and kitchen. Upstairs offer a full bath and three bedrooms. The basement is divided into two rooms for potential additional living space. Minutes from the hospital, shopping, and interstate access. Call now to schedule your private viewing.
